{"tid":2160412,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"健康碼破解方法 集思廣益","createTime":"2020-08-17T02:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T03:44:16.000Z","uid":58174,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6125f0b8ccfaa0b850c4c4c2e4ada1809376abfe","tid":2160412,"uid":58174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"仆街港共睇落會格硬推健康碼，如果到時要健康碼先返到工，睇怕大部分香港人都會照比DNA港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  如果健康碼冇得避，我覺得最簡單嘅破解方法就同朋友係交換驗，即係同朋友交換個樽驗，到時就唔會比港共知道你個DNA係咩，最好係比較疏嘅朋友等港共冇咁易估到個DNA係邊個<br />\n<br />\n  甚至可以同異性朋友交換，等政府知道佢得到嘅DNA一定唔係屬於你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aec8f3c132cd8328cd59369560c04582f9368d0","tid":2160412,"uid":58667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"搵一個人既口水比曬咁多人咪得"},{"pid":"a2517aa3036c431149879ee620e67a7d7372bb9c","tid":2160412,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"賣口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n$100/sample"},{"pid":"cc642ac0ce6821d68b3950559bdf23de9bcb580d","tid":2160412,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4b911db454a1bb345569c9b75e98c1e78ed889","tid":2160412,"uid":362492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc97ab3c01155d8004cadec7110020f04c6dd8cc","tid":2160412,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6125f0b8ccfaa0b850c4c4c2e4ada1809376abfe","tid":2160412,"uid":58174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"仆街港共睇落會格硬推健康碼，如果到時要健康碼先返到工，睇怕大部分香港人都會照比DNA港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  如果健康碼冇得避，我覺得最簡單嘅破解方法就同朋友係交換驗，即係同朋友交換個樽驗，到時就唔會比港共知道你個DNA係咩，最好係比較疏嘅朋友等港共冇咁易估到